com.yammer.metrics.core

类 NoOpExecutorService

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.yammer.metrics.core.NoOpExecutorService
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    Executor, ExecutorService, ScheduledExecutorService

    public class NoOpExecutorService
extends Object
implements ScheduledExecutorService
    An executor service that does nothing. Used with empty metrics so that no threads are created wasting time / space.
